### ===== PAYMENTS =====

### Get All Payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments

### Search Payments
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments?status=li|succeeded&order_name=created_at&order_direction=1

### Create Payment
POST {{baseUrl}}/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transaction_id": "TXN-001",
  "user_id": "3fa85f64-5717-4562-b3fc-2c963f66afa6",
  "amount": 10000,
  "currency": "USD",
  "status": "created",
  "provider_name": "stripe",
  "gateway_transaction_id": "ch_1234567890",
  "idempotency_key": "key-001"
}

### Get Payment by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}

### Update Payment
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "succeeded"
}

### Delete Payment
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/payments/{{paymentId}}

